data.description: Discover rustic luxury in this exquisite log home nestled on 20 acres. Greeted by a wrap-around porch, step inside to expansive living spaces: a spacious Family Room with an attached full bath, an Open-Concept Kitchen boasting a Double Oven, Large Island, and 5-burner Gas Range. Enjoy meals with loved ones in TWO generously-sized Dining Areas or cozy up beside the Two-Sided Fireplace. The Primary Suite, located on the main level, offers a Walk-in Closet and a welcoming bath with a Walk-in Shower. Features include Soaring Ceilings, Attached and Detached Garages, abundant Built-in Shelving, expansive Office, two cozy Sitting Rooms, and a vast Laundry Room/Mud Room with ample cabinetry. Outside, find a Gazebo perfect for tranquil evenings, Leaf Guard Gutters, sprawling yards and Pastures, a 26kw backup generator ensuring uninterrupted comfort, and the most impressive 40x90 commercial barn equipped with electricity, lean-tos, and outdoor water access.  Welcome Home!
